Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利桑那州卡特里那巡天天文台\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Catalina Sky Observatory in Arizona 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了以前从未见到过的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}notices something it hadn't seen before. 
