Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个对象非同寻常\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This object was special 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它可能会撞上地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because it was probably going to impact the Earth, 
