Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸听上去就像是音爆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That explosion would have sounded like a sonic boom. 
