Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学家希望该小行星的重量不足以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists had hoped the asteroid wasn't heavy enough 
