Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重创地面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and wreak havoc on the ground. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星跟踪了剧烈的爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Satellites track the fiery explosion, 
