Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.63,0:43:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括推进系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}including a propellant system 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.26,0:43:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以确保控制重返在水上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to ensure controlled re-entries over water. 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.01,0:43:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上 国际社会已同意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Basically, the international community has agreed 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.93,0:43:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重返可接受的风险水平约为万分之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that an acceptable level of risk for a re-entry is around one in 10,000. 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.10,0:43:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说 如果你有特定的重返1万次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That means that if you did a particular re-entry 10,000 times, 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.19,0:43:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其可能性就是你会击中地面上的一个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the likelihood is that you'll hit one person on the planet. 
