Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.69,0:43:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标就是把那块硬件重返到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the objective is that you should re-enter that piece of hardware 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.07,0:43:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全区域 比如大海里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into a safe area like the ocean. 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.95,0:43:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是新规则对已在太空中的数以千计的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But new guidelines won't have any effect 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.25,0:43:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老碎片并没有任何效果\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on the thousands of pieces of old debris already in space. 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.08,0:43:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸的是 我们大量的太空物体还是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Unfortunately, we have a number of objects in space still 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.59,0:43:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时设计并没有围绕着那个要求进行的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which were not designed when that requirement was around. 
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.59,0:44:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们仍然在缓缓降落\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And they still are slowly coming down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.05,0:44:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此其中某些东西奏效尚有段时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it'll be a while before some of these things take effect. 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.64,0:44:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已不再是科幻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's no longer a sci-fi fantasy. 
